log
@Add "mailest" 0.9.19

"mailest" is a new search backend for Mew using Hyper Estrairer.  It
is to replace the existing search backend "mewest".

OK gsoares ajacoutot
@
text
@"mailest" provides a search backend and id index database for Mew using
Hyper Estraier.

The major differences from the standard "mewest" are:

- monitors mail folders and updates the index automatically.
- keeps the database usable during updating the index.
@
